\DayZServer\mpmissions\dayzOffline.chernarusplus\custom

(if your server does not have a custom folder in your missions main directory, simply make one.)

Next, open your cfgeconomy.xml file and near the bottom, above the closing

</economycore>

tag, insert:

<ce folder="custom">
	<file name="Veh-Truck_01_Covered_Blue_Covered-complete-empty-cfgspawnabletypes.xml" type="spawnabletypes" />
	</ce>

If you are already using files to append your vanilla mission files, it should look something like this:

<ce folder="custom">
	<file name="some-other-types-file.xml" type="types" />
	<file name="some-other-events.xml" type="events" />
	<file name="Veh-Truck_01_Covered_Blue_Covered-complete-empty-cfgspawnabletypes.xml" type="spawnabletypes" />
	<file name="some-other-messages.xml" type="messages" />
	<file name="some-other-globals.xml" type="globals" />
	</ce>

Vailidate your edited files to check you haven't made any mistakes with https://www.xmlvalidation.com/

Restart your server.

Enjoy!

Dominus vobiscum! scalespeeder dayz 1.29 April 2026

